										The Calendo Team.
									</p>
								</td>
							</tr>
						</tbody>
					</table>
					<table width="600" align="center" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width:600px" valign="top">
    	            <tbody>
    	            	<tr>
		                	<td align="center">                    
								<p style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Calibri,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:normal;font-size:10px;color:#666">
								    You can also copy and paste the following link into your browser's address bar:<br>
								    <a target="_blank" style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Calibri,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:normal;color:#678d00;text-decoration:none" href="http://calendohq.com/registrations/complete/token-id">http://calendohq.com/registrations/complete/token-id</a>
								 </p>
						    	<p style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Calibri,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:normal;font-size:10px;color:#666">
