								</p>
								<p style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Calibri,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:normal;font-size:10px;color:#666">
								    <a target="_blank" style="font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Calibri,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:normal;color:#678d00;text-decoration:none" href="http://calendohq.com">Privacy Policy</a>
